{"an5.248:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.248 ","an5.248:0.2":"25. Duccaritavagga ","an5.248:0.3":"Dutiyamanoduccaritasutta ","an5.248:1.1":"“Pancime, bhikkhave, adinava manoduccarite …pe… anisamsa manosucarite. ","an5.248:1.2":"Katame panca? ","an5.248:1.3":"Attapi attanam na upavadati; ","an5.248:1.4":"anuvicca vinnu pasamsanti; ","an5.248:1.5":"kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggacchati; ","an5.248:1.6":"asaddhamma vutthati; ","an5.248:1.7":"saddhamme patitthati. ","an5.248:1.8":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, panca anisamsa manosucarite”ti. ","an5.248:1.9":"Atthamam. "}